Post to Facebook Watch live: House set to vote on bill to replace Obamacare The USA TODAY NETWORK will have live coverage of this event.  //usat.ly/2mUsASO   Watch live: House set to vote on bill to replace Obamacare USA TODAY NETWORK 10:10   The Capitol is seen at dawn on Jan. 18, 2017. (Photo:   AP) 4   
Thursday's expected House vote on a Republican health care bill to replace Obamacare is shaping up to be extremely close, with victory or defeat for the legislation potentially coming down to a handful of members. 
The exact time of the vote on the American Health Care Act is unknown, but you can watch the House Floor proceedings live in the player above. CLOSE
